Revenue

Revenue includes revenue from contracts with customers and revenue from leasing activities. In fiscal 2023 and 2022, lease revenue is €1,004 million and €1,104 million, respectively. In fiscal 2023 and 2022, Digital industries recognized €5,067 million and €4,691 million revenue, respectively, from its software business, Smart Infrastructure recognized €4,243 million and €3,856 million in its service business. Revenues of Mobility are mainly derived from construction-type business.